<P>5. A Special Chambers Application has been scheduled to deal with the treatment of disability tax credits, related to the Bankrupt's disabled child, claimed by the Bankrupt for pre-bankruptcy and bankruptcy tax years, but filed after the date of her discharge from bankruptcy;</P>
